f its kind in South Africa, Toast Event Festival will bring together a hand-picked selection of the best event industry professionals with those who believe in making every part of life a party to remember. This jaw-dropping experience will be hosted at the hottest entertainment venue, Sun Area, Time Square from 24 – 26 May 2019.We’ve identified 23 different categories addressing every aspect of event planning considering consumer and corporate audiences, from first time mommies to father of the bride.As every good party needs a special gift, visiting event connoisseurs (“Toasters” as we like to call them), will be given a warm welcome with a special tote bag crammed full of teaser products and vouchers to get them in the celebratory mood (limited to the first 1000 guests each day). “Toasters” will have the unique opportunity to meet with industry experts and learn some event planning secrets in the Inspiration Theatre, indulge in some tasters while enjoying live music at The Beat Box, see their dream outfit and style on The Runway or get some much needed table and décor inspiration directly from the professionals at The Table. Toast Event Festival promises to be an awe-inspiring bonanza of the absolute best in event planning with special Moments that are guaranteed to make any event unforgettable.Event specialists and professionals from all industries are invited to book their space now to be part of this event-planning extravaganza.View our launch video here and read more on www.toastfest.co.za.